	<div id="84193" class="singlecomment"><div class="commenthead">Patricia <div class="commentdate">January 23, 2008</div></div> <div class="commentbox"><p>I'm hosting a party this Saturday and I've been rummaging through a lot of recipes, trying to figure out what to serve to my guests that would be easy and painless. I really would hate to be the one stuck in the kitchen while everyone enjoys the party. </p>

<p>This recipe is definitely going to be served. But, I was just wondering, do you have any recipes that would go with this? I know this is already somewhat "heavy" considering that there's a generous amount of cheese, yogurt and tofu involved, so if you've got anything light in mind, I would love to hear what you're thinking. :) </p>

